  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t东京奥运会开幕式刚刚结束，看了下豆瓣虎扑微博等等网站。中国网友普遍认为东京开幕式超级阴森，很阴间，很寒酸，很拉胯。然后又集体回忆起了08北京奥运会开幕式。最后点火的时候，墙内人又开始讽刺日本用大阪直美这个有黑人血统的人来点火。不知日本国内是怎么看的？<br/>\n<br/>\n大家看了今天的开幕式吗？真有那么拉胯吗<br/>\n说实话我感觉的确是一般般，远不如我所期待的。但08年北京奥运会有那么神吗？<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9Talkya05NLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/SjY2kNM.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SjY2kNM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SjY2kNM.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9KY2s5UkZNLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jck9RFM.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jck9RFM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Jck9RFM.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9xcEJSWTZ4LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/qpBRY6x.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/qpBRY6x.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qpBRY6x.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9temxGQnNLLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/mzlFBsK.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/mzlFBsK.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mzlFBsK.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9GZ2t4Vkp2LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/FgkxVJv.png\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/FgkxVJv.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FgkxVJv.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
